#Juchitán, la cuidad de las mujeres, Instituto Oaxaqueño de las Culturas, Oaxaca 1997; 
#V.B-Th with Maria Mies, The Subsistence Perspective. Beyond the Globalised Economy, Zed Books, London 1999; 
#Geld oder Leben. Was uns wirklich reich macht, oekom, München, 2010 
#Bennholdt-Thomsen, Veronika, What Really Keeps our Cities Alive, Money or Subsistence? in: V.B-Th et al., eds, There Is an Alternative, 2001, pp. 217-233 
#Baier, Andrea/ Bennholdt-Thomsen, Veronika, The ‘Stuff’ of Which Social Proximity is Made, in: Kluge, Thomas/ Schramm, Engelbert, Hg., Regional Approaches to Sustainable Economy: Potentials and Limits, Experiences from German Case-Studies, Materialien Soziale Ökologie (MSÖ 19), ISOE, Frankfurt/M. 2002, pp. 10 – 17


